data.description: This wonderful property has SECONDARY IRRIGATION WATER.  The kitchen has corian countertops with lovely tile backsplash. There are plantation shutters in the living room and kitchen.  The home has two wood burning fireplaces, one brick and one rock.  The detached garage has a car hoist, is heated and is 1080 Sq. Ft. .  There is room for four cars in the garage. This home is a must see.
